guideData.title: guide for garrys 1
guideData.text_Content: Garry's Mod is a sandbox video game that allows players to create and manipulate objects and characters in a virtual environment. Developed by Garry Newman and published by Valve Corporation, Garry's Mod was originally released in 2004 as a modification for the game Half-Life 2. Today, Garry's Mod is a standalone game that has gained a large following of dedicated players who enjoy creating and sharing their own custom creations.

guideData.title: guide for garrys 2
guideData.text_Content: The first step to enjoying Garry's Mod is to download and install the game. You can purchase Garry's Mod on Steam, which is an online platform for buying and downloading video games. After purchasing and downloading the game, you can launch it from your Steam library.

guideData.title: guide for garrys 3
guideData.text_Content: Once you have launched Garry's Mod, you will be taken to the main menu where you can select various game modes, such as sandbox, darkrp, murder, and others. The sandbox mode is the most popular and allows you to create and manipulate objects in a virtual environment.

guideData.title: guide for garrys 4
guideData.text_Content: One of the core features of Garry's Mod is the ability to create and manipulate objects. To create an object, you will need to use the “duplicator” tool. The duplicator tool allows you to make copies of objects, which can then be manipulated and modified in various ways.

guideData.title: guide for garrys 5
guideData.text_Content: To access the duplicator tool, you will need to open the “Tools” menu, which can be found by clicking on the “Q” key. From the Tools menu, you can select the “duplicator” tool, which will allow you to create objects.

guideData.title: guide for garrys 6
guideData.text_Content: Once you have selected the duplicator tool, you can begin creating objects by clicking on an existing object and then clicking the “duplicate” button. You can then manipulate the duplicate object by using the mouse and keyboard. You can move, rotate, and scale the object as desired.

guideData.title: guide for garrys 7
guideData.text_Content: In addition to creating and manipulating objects, Garry's Mod also allows you to manipulate characters in various ways. To do this, you will need to use the “Physgun” tool. The Physgun tool allows you to pick up and manipulate characters in the same way that you can manipulate objects.
